title: Call or Text Totally rebuilt in 2012 with impact windows, new kitchen,
posting_body: ['Totally rebuilt in 2012 with impact windows, new kitchen, 3 new baths, new A/C, and close to downtown Oakland Parks entertainment district and 5 min walk to Wilton Manors.', 'Pool was diamond brighted and retiled back in 2012.', 'close to beaches the new sprouts market and I-95.', 'Aldis around the corner.', 'and public transportation available as well.', 'Best priced home in area.', 'will be freshly painted and front driveways will be pressure cleaned.', 'This home will not last.', 'Tenant moving out end of month, no showings till August 1, 2022 bring your small dogs also... 2 max with a small pet deposit.', '25 lb max', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'Helping people find rentals since 2012!', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'We specialize in Broward County Rentals.', 'I can text you a list of all the rentals available in the area.', 'Fast approval, NO HOA for some properties.', 'Pet friendly for some!', 'Proof of income is the most  important thing.', 'We can help people with bad credit or no credit!', "Let me know what you're looking for and I will find the right place regardless of the situation!", 'Brittini Flinn', 'SUN OCEAN REALTY', 'NO EMAIL', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'PLEASE REFER TO TYN103413581']
